WEBVTT

31:04.480 --> 31:05.240 line:80%
Are you...

31:05.680 --> 31:07.350 line:80%
taking over your father's business?

31:07.350 --> 31:09.080 line:80%
I have to make a living, don't I?

31:09.310 --> 31:10.370 line:80%
That's the spirit.

31:10.480 --> 31:11.590 line:80%
Don't listen to what others say.

31:10.600 --> 31:15.610 line:80%
[Li Deqin, Chef of Yixiang Restaurant]

31:11.800 --> 31:12.840 line:80%
What's wrong with butchering pigs?

31:12.840 --> 31:14.110 line:80%
Food makes no distinction
between men and women,

31:14.110 --> 31:15.640 line:80%
and neither does hard work.
